  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p>Beginning at 4th level in this class mod, you've put much more secure bindings on your Sealed Beast, allowing you to draw on more power without them escaping. However, this does not reduce the various downsides that arise from using so much foreign chakra as some become even more severe as you pass your previous limits. Inside your seal, the chains surrounding Sealed Beast become torii or iron bars. The mental cage which houses your beast gains additional locks and the chakra leaking out becomes a small stream.</p><p>Your Maximum Seal Bleed increases by 20, and the amount of Twisted Chakra you gain per Batch when making a Withdraw Check increases by 20. Also, if you succeed a Desperate Rage check, you can choose to not enter Controlled Rage. However, after succeeding the check, you can choose to end Desperate Rage as an Action on your turn at any time.</p>",
